-in-20235593.html?amp=1"><h3 class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-title">Zenith Insurance Paid N5bn Claims in 2023</h3></a></div></article></div><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 item"><article class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de container vertical-slider-container medium"><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de thumbnail"><a title="Credit Management Professionals Charged on Transparent Credit Appraisal" href="../../../2024/03/20/credit-management-professionals-charged-on-transparent-credit-appraisal5593?amp=1"><amp-img width="150" height="150" layout="fill" object-fit="cover" src="../../../../../global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/NICA.png" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de i-amphtml-layout-fill i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="fill"></amp-img></a></div><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-text"><a title="Credit Management Professionals Charged on Transparent Credit Appraisal" href="../../../2024/03/20/credit-management-professionals-charged-on-transparent-credit-appraisal5593?amp=1"><h3 class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-title">Credit Management Professionals Charged on Transparent Credit Appraisal</h3></a></div></article></div><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 item"><article class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de container vertical-slider-container medium"><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de thumbnail"><a title="Oyetola: FG Poised to Increase Eastern Ports’ Vessel Traffic " href="../../../2024/03/20/oyetola-fg-poised-to-increase-eastern-ports-vessel-traffic5593?amp=1"><amp-img width="150" height="150" layout="fill" object-fit="cover" src="../../../../../global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/Gboyega-Oyetola-800x450.gif" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de i-amphtml-layout-fill i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="fill"></amp-img></a></div><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-text"><a title="Oyetola: FG Poised to Increase Eastern Ports’ Vessel Traffic " href="../../../2024/03/20/oyetola-fg-poised-to-increase-eastern-ports-vessel-traffic5593?a